    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This engine features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis maintains its composure with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains structurally sound. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the longevity of the powertrain. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the kinematics of the five-link rear suspension and the hydraulic steering rack remain sharp and communicative. A well-sorted enthusiast's machine optimized for performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
