      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery remains supple and free of significant wear, while all electronic features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from a consistent service schedule, including a recent professional inspection, oil change, and a set of high-performance all-season tires with excellent tread depth. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision, offering a quiet and composed ride. Whether you are navigating city streets or embarking on a long-distance road trip, this car provides a confident and comfortable experience. Comprehensive service records are available to provide total peace of mind for the next owner.",
